extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em MusicLibrary], a website for a small music library.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The library has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Titles:] !{data.title_count}
      li #[strong Copies:] !{data.item_count}
      li #[strong Copies available:] !{data.item_available_count} 
      li #[strong Artists:] !{data.artist_count}
      li #[strong Genres:] !{data.genre_count}
      li #[strong Patrons:] !{data.patron_count}